Virtualenv is required for this project.
It ensures we are all using mutully compatible versions of packages.

Update your virtual env:

        ./make_env.sh

Activate env:

        . _env/bin/activate

Deactivate env (anywhere inside active env):

        deactivate

To install package issue (inside active environment):

        pip install <package>

(THIS WON'T PROPAGATE YOUR CHANGES TO OTHERS).

To propagate this to others do

        pip freeze > requirements.txt
        git add requirements.txt

Commit, push and ask your friends to rerun ./make_env

